_sText:
This map was originally from 2009, and was supposed to be the big map for KSF when Evolv and Untouch took over, however, the map came to a halt due to people not finishing their stages, was then left to rot for 15 years... until now.

The stages in this map now exist in other maps, there is also a bonus but it's too hard on my hands.

It is also worth mentioning this map was originally meant to be played similar to surf_elements, where you beat the stages in whatever order you wish to do them, however, I didn't do that in this version due to me not wanting to waste time on setting a logic counter up for a map no one is going to play seriously.

This map is NOT intended to be added to KSF now, due to the fact it's basically a rehash of already existing stages on maps. Many thanks to Unt0uch4bl3! If you are interested, read more about this maps history here: https://ksfclan.com/showthread.php?2486-OFFICIAL-KSF-surf-map%21-%28Updates-and-Status
